name: Memecoin Supercycle
description: What is $SUPR? 🚀 $SUPR is a memecoin launched on the Solana blockchain, inspired by the unstoppable Memecoin Supercycle — a phenomenon where crypto and memecoins thrive together. Unlike traditional PVP (player vs. player) competition between tokens, $SUPR is the community token for all memecoin communities, uniting everyone under one banner as the supercycle builds. More than just a coin, $SUPR is a movement to bring the memecoin world together, celebrating shared growth, collaboration, and community. 🌊💎 The storm is coming — are you ready? 🌩️🔥
